             </div>
             <div class="media-body">
              <h3>
               "A Holocaust Journey": Summer 2019 Study Abroad
              </h3>
              <em>
               "A Holocaust Journey": Summer 2019 Study Abroad
              </em>
              <br/>
              <i aria-hidden="true" class="fa fa-calendar">
              </i>
              <span class="date-display-single">
               October 1, 2018
              </span>
              <br/>
              <p>
               In summer 2019 we are organizing
               <a href="http://studyabroad.uncc.edu/index.cfm?FuseAction=Programs.ViewProgram&amp;Program_ID=11033">
                A Holocaust Journey
               </a>
               , our 6th annual Berlin &amp; Poland Study Abroad program and class, directed by Professor Judy LaPietra. The program will last from June 14-24 and will provide students an opportunity to study historical sites related to Holocaust history...
              </p>
              <p>
               <a alt=' "A Holocaust Journey": Summer 2019 Study Abroad' class="button button-green" href="/holocaust-journey-summer-2019-study-abroad" title=' "A Holocaust Journey": Summer 2019 Study Abroad'>
