             <div class="media-body">
              <h3>
               Global Studies Co-sponsors Series on Bosnian Elections
              </h3>
              <i aria-hidden="true" class="fa fa-calendar">
              </i>
              <span class="date-display-single">
               August 15, 2018
              </span>
              <br/>
              <p>
               "I want to show that our differences can be a source of strength instead of a cause for hatred and division” stated
               <a href="https://www.charlotteobserver.com/news/local/article209219999.html">
                Mirsad Hadžikadić
               </a>
               , UNCC professor who ran for president of Bosnia-Herzegovina in its October 7 elections. Bosnia was one of the six republics of Yugoslavia until that country was torn apart by...
              </p>
              <p>
               <a alt=" Global Studies Co-sponsors Series on Bosnian Elections" class="button button-green" href="/global-studies-co-sponsors-series-bosnian-elections" title=" Global Studies Co-sponsors Series on Bosnian Elections">
